short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Fiscal Date Calculator is an extension that accurately converts any calendar date you enter into its corresponding fiscal date.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension is designed to calculate the Fiscal Date based on any given date. Users can input a specific date, and the extension will determine the corresponding fiscal date, which is often used for financial and budgetary purposes by businesses and organizations. Simply enter a date, click the calculate button and it provides you with the fiscal date (month and year) for the entered date.
